            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Before getting the tour from Jim McEwen who knows the owner, Red, the  video team tours the junkyard with a drone - and this place is huge!  There are cars as far as the eye can see, and even cars stacked on cars  in some spots. Surprisingly, a lot of them look to be relatively solid  body machines. There’s everything on this almost 20 acre lot, muscle cars, sports cars, pony cars, classic SUVs, trucks, buses and delivery trucks.",
