          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The owner of the lot, Red, used to be a paint and body guy for many  years of his career, which potentially explains why there’s so many of  these cars ended up here - with many of them being turned into donor  cars for better condition examples of that model.",
